-- MOVES-BCS names Tim Bevan as chief executive of prime brokerage
-- 
-- Wed Oct 15, 2014 09:59AM EDT
-- None



Oct 15 (Reuters) - Financial services provider BCS Financial Group (BCS) named Tim Bevan as chief executive of BCS prime brokerage.

Bevan will be responsible for all international operations including future growth strategy, new products and diversifying the business, BCS said in a statement.